歸來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n歐盟快啲考慮下用Nokia嘅5G standard<br />\n話曬自己人公司<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然話事果個好想用屎為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望波蘭可以說服到更多國家咪撚用屎為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4673de154982f650e950d1c4d1b2c5c1305733b","tid":998333,"uid":35542,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f3a151c435098f0107b33d2e6bf85ce726445086","tid":998333,"uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"af37a4389ab84890b5c4454c71fe181831cf83e1","tid":998333,"uid":85116,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T01:51:55.000Z","msg":"其實5G係歐美嘅發展係點樣,以家聽親都係中國同韓國佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T04:42:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>美國已開始實用, 華文傳媒完全唔提<br />\n華文傳媒一直聲稱「華為5G領先全球」, 但我到今日都唔知佢領先緊D乜東東？</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">美國第一個5G服務已上線！AT&amp;T預計15GB月費台幣2,100元<br />\n2018.12.19</span><br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bnext.com.tw/article/51706/at&amp;t-launched-5g-in-12-cities\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bnext.com.tw%2Farticle%2F51706%2Fat%26t-launched-5g-in-12-cities&d=9c3%2BN5p%2FDKq6bgy07Hg5hgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=abc42efe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bnext.com.tw/article/51706/at&amp;t-launched-5g-in-12-cities</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://bnextmedia.s3.hicloud.net.tw/image/album/2016-10/img-1477294077-21351@900.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fbnextmedia.s3.hicloud.net.tw%2Fimage%2Falbum%2F2016-10%2Fimg-1477294077-21351%40900.jpg&h=a67a906e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n身為美國第一大電信商的AT&amp;T，宣布在美國12座城市正式上線5G網路給終端消費者使用，成為美國第一家上線5G行動數據網路的電信商。<br />\n<br />\n然而，在行動裝置尚未支援5G網路的情況下，AT&amp;T目前只先針對少數受挑選過的消費者，給予自家的熱點裝置，讓他們透過熱點裝置轉Wi-Fi，感受5G網路的速度。<br />\n<br />\nAT&amp;T的熱點裝置還不會正式發售，只會先以贈送方式，讓部分消費者感受新科技。此熱點裝置會在2019年春天正式販賣給所有消費者，到時候，首個5G使用方案則會採每月15GB用量要價70美元（約2,100元台幣）。<br />\n<br />\n雖然一切都還在初期使用階段，美國消費者對5G網路的認識也尚未全面普及，但AT&amp;T的技術通行以及初步方案擬定，卻也讓同業開始警覺：當終端裝置得開始支援5G網路，電信商該提供什麼樣的服務方案，才最切中消費者需求？<br />\n<br />\nAT&amp;T的5G網路目前已經在休士頓、亞特蘭大、達拉斯、紐奧良等城市中的部分區域上線，預計在未來6個月推出至洛杉磯、聖地牙哥、奧蘭多等地。AT&amp;T過去在鋪建5G網路時，就承諾會在2018年底上線，這次的發布，也實現了它的諾言。<br />\n<br />\n美國的四大電信商在5G網路上，都已經有初步行動。Verizon的5G TF網路在10月就已經上線，但因為並不是產業普遍認定的5G NR標準，會在明年透過韌體升級，正式通行5G網路；T-Mpbile的5G網路預定明年上線，而Sprint則預計在2019年上半年，開始販售支援5G的智慧型手機。<br />\n<br />\n這些電信商除了讓5G給予行動裝置較快速度的上網體驗外，也將開始鎖定家用網路，推行相關裝置與方案，讓快速的5G網路取代現有的家用寬頻網路服務。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T05:44:51.000Z","msg":"AT&amp;T個5G E係假5G，等於以前電訊商啱啱出LTE時話LTE=4G一樣<br />\n<a href=\"https://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2019/01/att-decides-4g-is-now-5g-starts-issues-icon-changing-software-updates/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Farstechnica.com%2Fgadgets%2F2019%2F01%2Fatt-decides-4g-is-now-5g-starts-issues-icon-changing-software-updates%2F&d=9c3%2BN5p%2FDKq6bgy07Hg5hgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=95a83465\" target=\"_blank\">https://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2019/01/att-decides-4g-is-now-5g-starts-issues-icon-changing-software-updates/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2019/1/7/18172355/att-fake-5g-logo-rolling-out-samsung-lg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2019%2F1%2F7%2F18172355%2Fatt-fake-5g-logo-rolling-out-samsung-lg&d=9c3%2BN5p%2FDKq6bgy07Hg5hgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=53dc2e40\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.theverge.com/2019/1/7/18172355/att-fake-5g-logo-rolling-out-samsung-lg</a>"},{"pid":"d5c6c1c9635c0bfc6188aa001d948749be4feb56","tid":998333,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4673de154982f650e950d1c4d1b2c5c1305733b","tid":998333,"uid":35542,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f3a151c435098f0107b33d2e6bf85ce726445086","tid":998333,"uid":79563,